        "title": "台灣已經解放惹！統促黨同志辦國慶慶典只被舉牌警告，毫髮無傷，爽歪歪",
        "body": "台湾统促党9月30日举办“欢欣鼓舞庆国庆”活动。活动现场，五星红旗随风飘扬，诠释统促党的“两岸一家亲，希望两岸统一”诉求。该集会举行期间遭到台北警方共6次警告，集会参与者在活动过程中曾遭警方4度举牌警告，统促党总裁张安乐到场后也遭2次警告。活动仍然坚持举办了2个多小时，直至下午3时被迫结束。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"aw-upload-img-list\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/uploads/questions/20181024/af970ba15bc6ffc27b023c99100f2752.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" data-fancybox-group=\"thumb\" rel=\"lightbox\"><img src=\"/uploads/questions/20181024/af970ba15bc6ffc27b023c99100f2752.jpg\" class=\"img-thumbnail\" alt=\"IMG_20181024_163227.jpg\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/uploads/questions/20181024/de8249f85f10afaad3daf9e7d1e13a80.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" data-fancybox-group=\"thumb\" rel=\"lightbox\"><img src=\"/uploads/questions/20181024/de8249f85f10afaad3daf9e7d1e13a80.jpg\" class=\"img-thumbnail\" alt=\"IMG_20181024_163225.jpg\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
